      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ARTISTIC SCOTT (4) has had tough barriers in stronger races in the last two outings so prepared to overlook those results. Better drawn and had won twice in a row prior, one of them here. ZEN MASTER (5) is fitter for recent racing and did a good job when fourth from the back row at his most recent appearance at Penrith. That form should measure up here. TIME TO DANCE NZ (2) is in good form with top-four finishes at his last five starts, most recently coming from wider to be beaten neck into second at Newcastle. Likely to get the favours from this nice draw so could break through. LAYLA SHANNON (1) did some work when midfield last time but had produced some good efforts prior including a second two back and a win at this circuit and distance last month. Drawn to advantage.",
